Why develop a UPR Implementation Plan
Developing a UPR Implementation Plan in preparation for the 2nd UPR Cycle is an innovative approach that Switzerland aims at creating since the UPR is a ground-breaking human rights mechanism that encourages States to conduct a public dialogue on human rights.
Purpose of the UPR Implementation Plan The purpose of the UPR Implementation Plan Activity Plan in this concrete Implementation Plan to re-embed Article 7 of the Vienna Declaration and Programme of Action in the human rights work of the Swiss Government Federal Administration. It aims at strengthening Swiss efforts
